her of Tekoa had two wives, Helah and Naarah.","year":-1721},{"id":"recwrmth62lWU4lEP","ref":"1Chr.4.6","text":"And Naarah bare him Ahuzam, and Hepher, and Temeni, and Haahashtari. These were the sons of Naarah.","year":-1721},{"id":"recO8f2rTxWhoVI01","ref":"1Chr.4.7","text":"And the sons of Helah were, Zereth, and Jezoar, and Ethnan.","year":-1721},{"id":"recuyB6KRFGKJuOFN","ref":"1Chr.4.8","text":"And Coz begat Anub, and Zobebah, and the families of Aharhel the son of Harum.","year":-1721}]}
